
 

'''Sisi Virginia Khampepe''' (O belegilwe ka 8 Pheregong 1957<ref name="cc" />) ke moahlodi wa Afrika Borwa yo a šomelagojudge  Constitutional Court of South Africa.

== Bophelo ==
Khampepe o belegetšwe Soweto. O hweditše dikiri ya B Proc kua  University of Zululand le LLM degree yagwe kua   Harvard Law School. O amogetšwe bjale ka Moemedi ka ngwaga wa 1985 , a šoma kua Bowman Gilfillan bjale ka mošomi sekhukhung, bjale ka moemedi wa labour law. ka1995 o kgethilwe bjalo ka leloka la Truth and Reconciliation Commission.<ref name="cc" />  Go together ka1999 o kgethilwe  bjalo kaDeputy National Director of Public Prosecutions go National Prosecuting Authority.<ref name="cc" />

== Letaetšano ==
Ka 2000 Khampepe o kgethilwe bjale ka Moahlodi wa Transvaal Provincial Division ya High Court, (e tsebegang gore ke Gauteng Division). Ka2007 o ile a kgethwa  kua Labour Appeal Court, le ka ngwaga wa 2009 o kgethilwe  kua Constitutional Court ka Mopresidente [[Jacob Zuma]]. ka 2021 o kgethilwe go itšoara ka chief justice ya apex court.

